"{\"uid\": \"citizen.co.za-sport-semenya-defence-intersex-boxers-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Home\\u00bbSport  ByWesley Botton  Chief sports journalist  3 minute read  6 August 2024  01:40 pm  Caster Semenya during a hearing at the European Court of Human Rights earlier this year.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\", \"score\": 0.901131173431149, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Botton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\"}, {\"begin\": 94, \"end\": 108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caster_Semenya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caster Semenya\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caster_Semenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caster_Semenya\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Picture: Frederick Florin/AFP  Two-time Olympic 800m champion Caster Semenya has called on international sporting authorities to standardise gender rules and protect intersex athletes from discrimination.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 192, \"end\": 201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.655650942865743e-17, \"text\": \"Frederick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\"}, {\"begin\": 209, \"end\": 212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999999047597657, \"rank\": 9.52396545057344e-08, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}, {\"begin\": 245, \"end\": 259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caster_Semenya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caster Semenya\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caster_Semenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caster_Semenya\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Semenya was banned from competing\\u00a0against women last year by World Athletics, along with other track athletes with differences of sexual development (DSD), a decision the South African star is still fighting in court.\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 606, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 450, \"end\": 465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1415566795984682e-16, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}, {\"begin\": 539, \"end\": 542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\", \"score\": 0.99994015504852, \"rank\": 5.984853317867407e-05, \"text\": \"DSD\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ALSO READ:Semenya hopes latest hearing will protect dignity of athletes  In some sports, however, DSD athletes are still able to compete, with Algeria's Imane Khelif and Taiwan's Lin Yu-ting receiving widespread criticism during the ongoingOlympic Gamesin Paris, where both athletes secured medals.\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 906, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 706, \"end\": 709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\", \"score\": 0.99994015504852, \"rank\": 5.984853317867407e-05, \"text\": \"DSD\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\"}, {\"begin\": 751, \"end\": 758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999921597850908, \"rank\": 7.148103230593115e-06, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 778, \"end\": 784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.9999230155775428, \"rank\": 7.289104153992889e-05, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}, {\"begin\": 787, \"end\": 798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}, {\"begin\": 864, \"end\": 869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999980048343681, \"rank\": 1.9951695517183887e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Though both boxers had been prevented from competing at the World Championships last year, after tests revealed they had unusually high testosterone levels, that event was organised by theInternational Boxing Association(IBA) which is no longer recognised by the International Olympic Committee\\u00a0(IOC).\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1171, \"end\": 1202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC organised the boxing tournament at theParis Games, clearing Khelif and Yu-ting to participate.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1215, \"end\": 1218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.212831934175075e-27, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While she had retired from competitive running, Semenya felt it was important that gender rules affecting DSD athletes were consistent across the various sports.\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1421, \"end\": 1424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\", \"score\": 0.99994015504852, \"rank\": 5.984853317867407e-05, \"text\": \"DSD\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What happened at the Olympics now is not what happened in my space.\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1546, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Each organisation has its own policy.\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Boxing has its own and athletics has its own,\\\" Semenya said in an interview withSportsBoom.\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1676, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not about what I want, but about principles of life.\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1736, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My views are not about me because I have ventured more into coaching now.\\\"\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1811, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Semenya defended Algerian fighter Khelif, who had\\u00a0taken the brunt of criticism on social media, with many people incorrectly claiming she was transgender and calling for sporting authorities to ensure women were protected, particularly in contact sports.\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 2067, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1830, \"end\": 1838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9820219849172446, \"rank\": 0.018235032417059933, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Imane is a great boxer and people always criticise when someone is doing well,\\\" Semenya said.\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2163, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People will always talk then.\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2195, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When she wasn't winning, then everyone was quiet.\\\"\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is so Painful to watch.\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2276, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been boxing for years in the International Boxing Association which has committed INJUSTICE towards me.~#Imane_Khelifpic.twitter.com/NH7GeM9YoK  The debate around intersex athletes was far from over, but Semenya called on the IOC to protect them against discrimination.\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2553, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2313, \"end\": 2345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.222205998613411e-19, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2510, \"end\": 2513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.212831934175075e-27, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The IOC's policy and constitution should not contradict each other,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2634, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2560, \"end\": 2563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.212831934175075e-27, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sport is for all people and the constitution says no to discrimination, but the minute they allow women to be disgraced, it confuses us.\\\"\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2774, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Add The Citizen as a Preferred Source on Google and follow us on Google News to see more of our trusted reporting in Google News and Top Stories.\", \"from\": 2776, \"to\": 2921, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2817, \"end\": 2823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9452013415354464, \"rank\": 0.057975396768424906, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 2841, \"end\": 2852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google News\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\"}, {\"begin\": 2893, \"end\": 2904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google News\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"dbpedia\"